The paper deals with image captioning, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed model is a convolutional neural network (CNN), which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the evaluation is done on benchmark datasets, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM).
